1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to the Commission for the Blind and Visually
2 Impaired; to amend section 71-8616, Reissue Revised Statutes of
3 Nebraska; to provide for development of a statewide support service
4 provider program for deaf-blind persons; to state intent regarding
5 appropriations; to eliminate obsolete provisions; to repeal the
6 original section; and to declare an emergency.
7 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
